<collectingRegion box="[1108,1211,1546,1570]" country="Trinidad and Tobago" name="San Juan/Laventille" pageId="124" pageNumber="124">San Juan</collectingRegion>
(table 54). Most roosting groups of this species were encountered at ground level, but one individual was said (by the Matses hunter who collected it) to have been found roosting high up inside a large hollow tree; possibly it had been
